TITLE OF SECTION

T.S. Eliot
  became jolly at
the slightest hint
  of chocolate mint.

> There once was a fellow whose coding
> was subject to serious bloating[bl]:
>  he blow up his stack
>  in a service attack
> and they found him in transit, uploading.
